  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink81-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">taṉṉaik koṭumai kūṟiṉāḷ talaimakaḷ eṉpatu kēṭṭa parattai talaimakaṉ vantu
          taṉmēl aṉpuṭaimai kuṟiṉāṉāka avaṭkup pāṅkāyiṉār kēṭpac colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="Aink81">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>kurukuṭait tuṇṭa veḷḷakaṭ ṭiyāmai</l>
          <l>yarippaṟai viṉaiña ralkumicaik kūṭṭu</l>
          <l>malaraṇi vāyiṟ poykai yūranī</l>
          <l>yeṉṉai nayantaṉe ṉeṉṟiniṉ</l>
          <l>maṉaiyōḷ kēṭkiṉ varuntuvaḷ peritē.</l>
        </lg>
  
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

<l>         O man from a village with a pond </l> 
<l rend="indent4">         whose mouth is adorned with flowers</l> 
<l rend="indent4">               [and] where labourers working [to the sound] of the drum at harvest time</l> 
<l rend="indent4">               bring to the hill where they are staying </l> 
<l rend="indent4">                   tortoises whose white bellies </l> 
<l rend="indent4">                   have already been smashed and eaten by a heron! </l> 
<p/>
<l>       If your wife hears </l> 
<l>       that you've said you want me, </l> 
<l>       she will suffer greatly. </l> 


      </lg>

    </div>
